[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_985085'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_985085'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #2 于:</strong> 2019-03-22, 周五 22:12:47 &#187;</div>
